  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Lord Evans wrote to the Shadow Home Secretary, Nick Thomas-Symonds MP, replying to his request that CSPL undertake an investigation. </p>

