      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>Shadow Home Secretary, Nick Thomas-Symonds MP, <a rel="external" href="https://twitter.com/NickTorfaen/status/1329668360624345089?s=20" class="govuk-link">wrote to Lord Evans asking CSPL to undertake an investigation into allegations that the Home Secretary breached the Ministerial Code in relation to bullying and harassment.</a> Lord Evans responded making clear that the CSPL is not a regulator and cannot undertake investigations into individual cases.</p>
</div>

</div>
